## Register (create)

Register a new user.  Returns the user object.

    POST /register

### Input

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
`email` | `string` | **Required**
`password` | `string` |  **Required**


### Output

<%= json :user %>


## Login

Retrieve an auth token for the specified user.  See [Authentication](/authentication) for how to use it.

    POST /login

### Input

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
`email` | `string` | **Required**
`password` | `string` | **Required**

### Output

<%= json :auth_token %>


## Login Facebook

Retrieve an auth token for the user using facebook.  Will create the user if they don't already exist.

    POST /login/facebook

### Input

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
`token` | `string` | Access token retrieved from facebook SDk.


## Me

Get the currently logged in user.

    GET /users/me

## Change Password

Change the password of the currently logged in user.

    POST /users/change-password

### Input

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
`current_password` | `string` **Required**
`new_password` | `string`  **Required**


